				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Type: activated
<br />
Duration: 30 minutes
<br />
Refresh: 15 minutes
<br />
Description: Pet shares the buffs of it's owner in addition to it's individual buffs.
<br />

<br />

<br />
I know a lot of people have suggested exactly this - but without a refresh timer or some means to prevent chain casting pets with raid buffs.  There needs to be some form of abuse prevention.
<br />

<br />
